full_description.en:
**Make sure your portfolio allocation matches your willingness and ability to take risks.**

When you build a portfolio, one of the first decisions to make is choosing how much of your money you want to invest in equities vs. bonds. The Risk Profile power up calculates and shows you your equity vs bond ratio and matches you to one of our 5 Risk Profiles.

**Which one are you?**

We will match your current portfolio with one of our 5 risk profiles. Does your current portfolio allocation match your personal risk profile?

Compare your portfolio allocation with the risk profile you feel best fits your personality.  Prepare your future buys and sells to make sure your portfolio matches your risk profile.

If your portfolio is in line with your desired risk profile, make sure it remains on track and rebalance your portfolio regularly to keep an equity vs bonds ratio that matches.
